      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "KOMODO (7) overcame a wide draw on the back row to get home by a narrow margin at his latest appearance at this venue. Deserved that on the back of consistent form. The driver has some work to do from this wide starting position but he is a leading hope again with even luck. THESTATESMAN (4) made a good return in coming from the back row for third here last time out. Fitter so can progress off that. ZENARIO (9) ended his last campaign with a placing at Listed level in SA. Has won four of seven tries at this distance. Keep safe fresh. RUFF NUT (5) has not raced since November's Vicbred Super Series where he was runner-up in the heats. Looks forward enough for the return after a minor placing in a recent trial. TEN DA TOUCH NZ (6) is a player again having added to a string of top-four finishes with a respectable third at his most recent appearance here.",
